				<h1>Corner Unit.<br>Huge Yard.</h1>
				<div class="hero-address">8020 Linda Vista Rd, Unit 1C<br>San Diego, CA 92111</div>
				<div class="hero-price">$549,000</div>
				<a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Schedule a Showing</a>
